{"tid":2153781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國外相：改期危險　反而在選完再選的過程中會鞏固香港的民主","createTime":"2020-08-12T17:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T18:22:36.000Z","uid":261647,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"58ded21c0ac78c82b795542cb5a22236a95e17d3","tid":2153781,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/3264451250317592/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.326590167437063%2F3264451250317592%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7UYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=9e66b94c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/3264451250317592/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tup24BF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftup24BF.png&h=56f9fe8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會改期史<br />\n<br />\n面對有機會被未來民選立法會推翻政府議案及財政預算，港督尤德曾於85年提議將立法會會期改為三年一屆 (3-year interval)，以換取當年取消《香港憲法》中政府直接具解散議會的保留權力，目的是為了防止1997後特區政府會進行無限「DS」(解散) 「不合作」的立法會。<br />\n<br />\n時任英國外相賀維 (Geoffrey Howe) 向英國首相戴卓爾夫人匯報此事，直指改選舉時間的行徑比起運用DS權，對他來說是一個「更加危險」與「可擴展」的先例 (a more dangerous and open-ended precedent)，並不可取。<br />\n<br />\n賀維更稱與其改期，不如就讓特區政府進行無限DS，反而在選完再選的過程中會鞏固香港的民主 (Democracy within the SAR would thus stand to be strengthened rather than weakened)。"},{"pid":"e72629ad6676c94614a542166e1402ac34cc8e25","tid":2153781,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:04:42.000Z","msg":"請支持本土研究社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6590f574a48f1856d9a131d44e8fbe4c425efdd4","tid":2153781,"uid":143183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e72629ad6676c94614a542166e1402ac34cc8e25","tid":2153781,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:04:42.000Z","msg":"請支持本土研究社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:17:49.000Z","msg":"一定係"},{"pid":"42c40943c4e5fa0bda4d957125ba81f306786cf8","tid":2153781,"uid":143183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:18:28.000Z","msg":"改期一定係最壞"},{"pid":"488bfebb243d6fbdac271ac8f5381b3ca15046d7","tid":2153781,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:22:36.000Z","msg":"可惜 中共從來都打橫黎"}]}